    <dsc type="combined">
      <head>Contents List</head>
      <c01 level="series" id="d1e168">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Portraits of Richard Harding
               Davis</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>9 portrait illustrations, clipped from an article in
               an unidentified magazine.</p>
        </scopecontent>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e175">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 5" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">July, 1869</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e183">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 9" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1873</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e191">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 18" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1888</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>With his brother Charles Belmont Davis, the
                  present Consul to Florence, Italy. Photograph taken
                  at Lehigh University.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e202">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 22" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1886</unitdate></unittitle>
          </did>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e208">
          <did>
            <unittitle>Richard Harding Davis in disguise 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">n.d.</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>In this photograph, Davis is "in the disguise of a
                  burglar, under which, as a reporter for the 
                  <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">Press</title>, he lived among
                  the thieves of Philadelphia."</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e222">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 24" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1888</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>"A reporter on the New York 
                  <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">Evening Sun</title>. From a
                  photograph by William M. Ruschhaupt, New York."</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e236">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 26" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1890</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>"Gathering material for 
                  <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">The West from a Car
                  Window</title>."</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e250">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"At the present time, age 29" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">[1893]</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>"From a photograph by Pach."</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="subseries" id="d1e261">
          <did>
            <unittitle>"Age 29" 
                  <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">[1893]</unitdate></unittitle>
            <container label="Box" type="Box">16</container>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>Not identical to the preceding image, but
                  apparently taken at the same sitting.</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
      </c01>
    </dsc>
